{
  "texts": [
    "This broadbased approach ensured that we didn't overlook any relevant digital libraries.",
    "We employed pertinent keywords to pinpoint suitable published articles.",
    "Moreover, we used snowballing data sampling to gather potential literature related to our research objective.",
    "This involved scrutinizing reference sections of relevant publications (backward snowballing) and exploring studies citing our selected literature (forward snowballing) (Wohlin 2014).",
    "This strategy resulted in a continuously expanding sample size as we delved deeper into references and citations (Wohlin 2014)."
  ]
}